<a class=hero-cta-secondary href=/contact/>Get in touch →</a></div><div class=hero-social><a class=social-link href=https://x.com/tkachuk_science target=_blank rel=noopener aria-label="X (formerly Twitter)"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-4.714-6.231-5.401 6.231H2.74l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
<span>X</span>
